name: arabinose-5-phosphate isomerase
classes: Interconverting aldoses and ketoses, and related compounds
comment: The enzyme is involved in the pathway for synthesis of 3-deoxy-D-manno-octulosonate (Kdo), a component of bacterial lipopolysaccharides and plant call walls.
